* The library is still using some locale-dependent functions:

  + __ctype_b_loc
  + __ctype_tolower_loc
  + __ctype_toupper_loc
  + iswalnum
  + iswctype
  + iswlower
  + strcasecmp
  + towlower
  + towupper
  + wcscoll
  + wctype

* Use the DFA decoder: http://bjoern.hoehrmann.de/utf-8/decoder/dfa

